	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>One way to think of zen is this: a total state of focus that incorporates a total togetherness of body and mind. Zen is a way of being. It also is a state of mind ( https://www.urbandictionary.com)</p>
<p>Zensark tries to bring these same principles of zen to building software</p>
<p>Zensark is a technology services company with a footprint in the US and India. Zensark brings over a decade of experience in software development, integration, strategy development, and deployment. Zensark started its journey by building healthcare related software and services. In the last 18 months, aligning to changing business landscape and new opportunities, Zensark has forayed into solving new age business problems in fields such as Voice Analytics, Conversational AI and Video Interviews.</p>
<p>Zensark has rich experience in product engineering consulting for startups and SMBs, taking them from idea to POC to Prototype to Product. We specialize in the early perception of business use cases and potential applications of new technology. We offer custom application development as well as production support for existing solutions.</p>

